(23545, 'Neximerican 40 mg 21 caps.', 'نيكسيمريكان 40مجم 21 كبسولة', '', '79', 'Esomeprazole', 'Medizen pharmaceutical industries > paxal pharmaceutical', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', 'مضاد للحموضة ولعلاج حرقان الصدر وقرحة المعدة وارتجاع المريء', 'Peptic ulcer.proton pump inhibitor', '40 mg', 'Esomeprazole is indicated for the treatment of acid-reflux disorders including healing and maintenance of erosive esophagitis, and symptomatic gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD), peptic ulcer disease, H. pylori eradication, prevention of gastrointestinal bleeds with NSAID use, and for the long-term treatment of pathological hypersecretory conditions including Zollinger-Ellison Syndrome.', '6224011379021', '', 3917, '2022-08-01', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(31792, 'Andomatoid 4 mg 28 f.c.tabs.', 'اندوماتويد 4مجم 28 قرص', '', '2,200', 'Baricitinib', 'Eva pharma > andalous pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'لعلاج التهاب المفاصل الروماتويدي حيث يعمل عن طريق تقليل نشاط الجهاز المناعي.', 'Janus kinase (jak) inhibitor', '4 mg', 'In the US and Europe, baricitinib is indicated for the treatment of adult patients with moderately to severely active rheumatoid arthritis who have had an inadequate response to one or more TNF blockers. Baricitinib may be used as monotherapy or in combination with [methotrexate] [L41760,L41770] or other DMARDs.[L41760]
